<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why, you...!</b></font>

123
00:06:43,014 --> 00:06:45,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way, let's have a little talk.</b></font>

124
00:06:45,444 --> 00:06:49,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Next Saturday, maybe you could
