144
00:07:51,744 --> 00:07:53,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Will you run, Iketani?</b></font>

145
00:07:53,384 --> 00:07:56,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. I'll run the downhill.</b></font>

146
00:07:56,584 --> 00:07:59,924
