148
00:08:01,524 --> 00:08:04,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One mistake on the downhill can be fatal.</b></font>

149
00:08:04,364 --> 00:08:05,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I understand.</b></font>

150
00:08:05,664 --> 00:08:09,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I understand, but I have to
