152
00:08:35,224 --> 00:08:37,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That Eight-Six...</i></b></font>

153
00:08:37,024 --> 00:08:38,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It hasn't appeared today, either.</i></b></font>

154
00:08:38,924 --> 00:08:41,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Maybe the driver wasn't a local?</i></b></font>

155
00:08:41,394 --> 00:08:45,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No, that's impossible. He was totally</i>
<i>familiar with this mountain.</i></b></font>

156
00:08:45,504 --> 00:08:48,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I want to face him again.</i>
<i>If I don't get my revenge,</i></b></font>

157
00:08:48,774 --> 00:08:50,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>then I won't calm down!</i></b></font>

158
00:08:50,774 --> 00:08:52,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Show yourself...</i></b></font>

159
00:08:52,244 --> 00:08:53,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...Ghost of Akina.</i></b></font>

160
00:08:53,674 --> 00:08:55,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't give a damn about the Speed Stars.</i></b></font>

161
00:08:55,774 --> 00:08:58,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I came here to face you.</i></b></font>

162
00:09:01,984 --> 00:09:06,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! The one and only Drift King,
Keiichi Tsuchiya! I can't believe it!</b></font>

163
00:09:06,524 --> 00:09:09,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It looks like he can control it
just by using the gas pedal.</b></font>

164
00:09:10,824 --> 00:09:11,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...</b></font>

165
00:09:11,994 --> 00:09:16,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you wish we could go out
right now and drift just like this?</b></font>

166
00:09:16,634 --> 00:09:20,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Sure.
--Check out this drift! Awesome!</b></font>

167
00:09:20,234 --> 00:09:22,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure.</b></font>

168
00:09:22,574 --> 00:09:24,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...</b></font>

169
00:09:24,544 --> 00:09:26,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure.</b></font>

170
00:09:26,974 --> 00:09:30,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! You keep saying, "Sure. Sure."
Do you even know what drift is?</b></font>

171
00:09:30,884 --> 00:09:33,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure, I know what drift is.</b></font>

172
00:09:33,544 --> 00:09:37,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, then, can you tell us what it is?</b></font>

173
00:09:37,584 --> 00:09:39,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In a curve...</b></font>

174
00:09:39,254 --> 00:09:41,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't say "curve." It's not cool.</b></font>

175
00:09:41,694 --> 00:09:45,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Street racers say "corner."</b></font>

176
00:09:45,064 --> 00:09:47,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, in a corner...</b></font>

177
00:09:47,734 --> 00:09:50,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...you make the front tires slide</b></font>

178
00:09:50,164 --> 00:09:52,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so that the car won't face the inside.</b></font>

179
00:09:52,564 --> 00:09:54,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

180
00:09:57,574 --> 00:09:59,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a good one, Takumi!</b></font>

181
00:09:59,574 --> 00:10:02,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the front tires are sliding,
that's called "understeer,"</b></font>

182
00:10:02,614 --> 00:10:05,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>which is totally uncool
and for people with no skill.</b></font>

183
00:10:05,444 --> 00:10:07,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A true drift isn't in the front--</b></font>

184
00:10:07,754 --> 00:10:09,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's in the rear.</b></font>

185
00:10:09,614 --> 00:10:11,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're really funny.</b></font>

186
00:10:11,524 --> 00:10:15,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--That was great, Takumi!
--It definitely was!</b></font>

187
00:10:15,354 --> 00:10:18,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Iketani, you're the one</i>
<i>who doesn't understand.</i></b></font>

188
00:10:18,264 --> 00:10:20,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>While in the middle of a drift,</i></b></font>

189
00:10:20,124 --> 00:10:22,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>the car is basically understeering.</i></b></font>

190
00:10:22,694 --> 00:10:25,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That was the highly advanced answer of those</i></b></font>

191
00:10:25,734 --> 00:10:27,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>who have mastered the four-wheel drift.</i></b></font>

192
00:10:27,904 --> 00:10:30,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm impressed.</i></b></font>

193
00:10:30,774 --> 00:10:34,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Customers are here! Get to work.</b></font>

194
00:10:34,144 --> 00:10:36,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, sir!</b></font>

195
00:10:36,274 --> 00:10:39,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Welcome!
--Welcome!</b></font>

196
00:10:47,284 --> 00:10:48,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>An FD...</i></b></font>

197
00:10:48,754 --> 00:10:50,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Could it be Keisuke Takahashi?</i></b></font>

198
00:10:53,464 --> 00:10:55,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>High octane, fill it up.</b></font>

199
00:10:55,294 --> 00:10:56,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, sir.</b></font>

200
00:11:04,204 --> 00:11:07,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a real enthusiast.</b></font>

201
00:11:10,014 --> 00:11:13,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. I thought I had seen
that S13 somewhere before...</b></font>

202
00:11:13,714 --> 00:11:15,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Speed Stars.</b></font>

203
00:11:22,894 --> 00:11:25,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can I ask you one thing?</b></font>

204
00:11:25,364 --> 00:11:28,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'd be the one who'd know...</b></font>

205
00:11:28,064 --> 00:11:30,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is there a ghost on Mt. Akina?</b></font>

206
00:11:30,594 --> 00:11:34,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The ghost of a super fast Eight-Six.</b></font>

207
00:11:37,474 --> 00:11:40,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow. Is he planning to fly with this?</b></font>

208
00:11:40,544 --> 00:11:44,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please don't joke around with me, sir.</b></font>

209
00:11:44,944 --> 00:11:47,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The part about the ghost was a joke,</b></font>

210
00:11:47,454 --> 00:11:49,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it's a black-and-white panda Trueno.</b></font>

211
00:11:49,814 --> 00:11:51,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the outside, it's a normal Eight-Six...</b></font>

212
00:11:51,784 --> 00:11:54,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but inside, it's an incredible monster.</b></font>

213
00:11:54,554 --> 00:11:58,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way a local like
you doesn't know about it.</b></font>

214
00:12:00,224 --> 00:12:01,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, fine then.</b></font>

215
00:12:01,564 --> 00:12:04,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If that's your secret weapon
for this Saturday's meet,</b></font>

216
00:12:04,934 --> 00:12:07,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>then I just got my wish.</b></font>

217
00:12:07,034 --> 00:12:09,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tell the driver of that Eight-Six</b></font>

218
00:12:09,834 --> 00:12:13,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that I won't lose to the same guy twice.</b></font>

219
00:12:13,904 --> 00:12:15,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The reason I lost last time</b></font>

220
00:12:15,374 --> 00:12:18,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is because I didn't know
the course and I got careless.</b></font>

221
00:12:19,614 --> 00:12:21,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks for coming.</b></font>

222
00:12:23,014 --> 00:12:25,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Keisuke Takahashi lost?</i></b></font>

223
00:12:25,584 --> 00:12:26,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What did he mean?</i></b></font>

224
00:12:26,924 --> 00:12:30,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't know anything about such an Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

225
00:12:33,424 --> 00:12:34,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Could it be...?</i></b></font>

226
00:12:34,894 --> 00:12:38,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six I saw at Takumi's house</i></b></font>

227
00:12:38,604 --> 00:12:40,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>was a panda Trueno.</i></b></font>

228
00:12:40,604 --> 00:12:43,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Was the boss telling the truth?</i></b></font>

229
00:12:43,634 --> 00:12:47,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The fastest on the downhill</i>
<i>is still that Eight-Six?</i></b></font>

230
00:12:58,154 --> 00:13:00,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Green Shopping Street"</b></font>

231
00:13:26,684 --> 00:13:29,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right, that's it for today.</b></font>

232
00:13:36,454 --> 00:13:38,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't this a lot more than usual?</b></font>

233
00:13:38,624 --> 00:13:41,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's fine. Just don't spill any.</b></font>

234
00:13:41,094 --> 00:13:43,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know.</b></font>

235
00:14:33,184 --> 00:14:35,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your face is sleepy as usual, Takumi.</b></font>

236
00:14:35,754 --> 00:14:39,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, but I was born with this face.</b></font>

237
00:14:39,524 --> 00:14:43,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't forget the Eight-Six on Saturday.</b></font>

238
00:14:43,754 --> 00:14:46,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know. You're so persistent, Itsuki.</b></font>

239
00:14:46,394 --> 00:14:50,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I don't make sure about it,
you might back out on me.</b></font>

240
00:14:50,594 --> 00:14:53,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please, Saturday, come quickly!</b></font>

241
00:14:53,364 --> 00:14:55,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm totally excited!</b></font>

242
00:14:55,374 --> 00:14:58,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, if both of us aim to become street racers,</b></font>

243
00:14:58,704 --> 00:15:02,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>maybe someday we'll be
known as the fastest on Akina.</b></font>

244
00:15:02,144 --> 00:15:05,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't really care either way.</b></font>

245
00:15:05,184 --> 00:15:08,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, even if you tried,
it'd be hopeless for you.</b></font>

246
00:15:08,314 --> 00:15:11,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After seeing you scream in
the back seat of Iketani's car,</b></font>

247
00:15:11,324 --> 00:15:13,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's obvious you don't have an ounce of talent.</b></font>

248
00:15:13,924 --> 00:15:15,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I'm different!</b></font>

249
00:15:15,654 --> 00:15:17,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was a little bit scared,</b></font>

250
00:15:17,764 --> 00:15:21,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I was able to look at the
corner exit with my teeth clenched.</b></font>

251
00:15:21,234 --> 00:15:23,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even Iketani has faith in me!</b></font>

252
00:15:23,494 --> 00:15:28,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He must think Takumi is hopeless,
but I have a bright future!</b></font>

253
00:15:29,534 --> 00:15:31,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? Takumi?</b></font>

254
00:15:31,444 --> 00:15:32,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

255
00:15:32,944 --> 00:15:36,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi! Takumi, wait a second!</b></font>

256
00:15:36,674 --> 00:15:39,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong with you? I know
you're jealous of my talent,</b></font>

257
00:15:39,514 --> 00:15:41,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but aren't you being a bit cold?</b></font>

258
00:15:41,284 --> 00:15:43,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not...</b></font>

259
00:15:43,514 --> 00:15:48,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And then Rumiko told my boyfriend
all about it. He got really mad!</b></font>

260
00:15:48,054 --> 00:15:49,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I saw.</b></font>

261
00:15:49,294 --> 00:15:51,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You like that kind of stuff?</b></font>

262
00:15:51,394 --> 00:15:52,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course not!</b></font>

263
00:15:52,694 --> 00:15:56,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must be a crime to let them
make their skirts that short.</b></font>

264
00:15:56,864 --> 00:15:59,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The school should make a new rule...</b></font>

265
00:16:01,234 --> 00:16:03,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Lucky!</b></font>

266
00:16:07,504 --> 00:16:09,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good morning, Takumi!</b></font>

267
00:16:09,674 --> 00:16:12,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mogi?!</b></font>

268
00:16:12,044 --> 00:16:14,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right. I have to talk
to you about something.</b></font>

269
00:16:14,754 --> 00:16:18,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come along, quickly!</b></font>

270
00:16:18,654 --> 00:16:22,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is this?! What the hell is going on here?!</b></font>

271
00:16:24,324 --> 00:16:26,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong?</b></font>

272
00:16:26,994 --> 00:16:30,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well... I...</b></font>

273
00:16:30,234 --> 00:16:34,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's something I want to tell you.</b></font>

274
00:16:34,574 --> 00:16:36,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it?</b></font>

275
00:16:38,444 --> 00:16:40,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well...</b></font>

276
00:16:40,174 --> 00:16:43,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I...</b></font>

277
00:16:43,074 --> 00:16:45,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bought a new bathing suit!</b></font>

278
00:16:45,344 --> 00:16:47,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's totally cute.</b></font>

279
00:16:47,584 --> 00:16:49,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that what you wanted to tell me?</b></font>

280
00:16:49,784 --> 00:16:51,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bingo.</b></font>

281
00:16:51,354 --> 00:16:56,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was so happy that I just had
to tell somebody about it!</b></font>

282
00:16:56,524 --> 00:16:59,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wanna see it? Are you
wondering what color it is?</b></font>

283
00:16:59,224 --> 00:17:00,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You want to see it soon, right?</b></font>

284
00:17:00,994 --> 00:17:03,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I want to, but...</b></font>

285
00:17:03,494 --> 00:17:05,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll let you see as much as you like</b></font>

286
00:17:05,404 --> 00:17:07,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>when we go to the ocean, okay?</b></font>

287
00:17:07,234 --> 00:17:11,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Until then, just... you... wait... and... see.</b></font>

288
00:17:11,004 --> 00:17:13,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about this Sunday? Are you free?</b></font>

289
00:17:13,904 --> 00:17:16,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. I have a break from work.</b></font>

290
00:17:16,644 --> 00:17:18,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, it's decided. It's a promise.</b></font>

291
00:17:18,914 --> 00:17:21,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A promise should never be broken.</b></font>

292
00:17:21,384 --> 00:17:23,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are only two kinds of people that I hate.</b></font>

293
00:17:23,484 --> 00:17:25,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>People who break their promises
and people who smoke.</b></font>

294
00:17:47,404 --> 00:17:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Damn. It's too tough.</i></b></font>

295
00:17:50,074 --> 00:17:53,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The corners that I never thought of as corners</i></b></font>

296
00:17:53,344 --> 00:17:56,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>are becoming more and more dreadful.</i></b></font>

297
00:17:56,014 --> 00:17:58,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>These corners that I am so familiar with</i></b></font>

298
00:17:58,184 --> 00:18:00,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>have now begun to show their fangs!</i></b></font>

299
00:18:22,744 --> 00:18:26,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's no use. Even if I push myself to the limit,</i></b></font>

300
00:18:26,584 --> 00:18:28,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't cut my times down.</i></b></font>

301
00:18:28,884 --> 00:18:32,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I thought that if I gave it more throttle,</i>
<i>I could cut my times down.</i></b></font>

302
00:18:32,324 --> 00:18:34,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But it's not that simple.</i></b></font>

303
00:18:34,384 --> 00:18:38,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is this the limit of my technique?</i></b></font>

304
00:18:38,194 --> 00:18:42,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's no way I can compete with them.</i></b></font>

305
00:18:45,734 --> 00:18:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello! Excuse me!</b></font>

306
00:18:50,074 --> 00:18:51,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?!</b></font>

307
00:18:53,944 --> 00:18:55,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me!</b></font>

308
00:18:55,514 --> 00:18:58,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can hear you. Give me a minute.</b></font>

309
00:18:58,584 --> 00:19:00,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure.</b></font>

310
00:19:01,314 --> 00:19:03,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome.</b></font>

311
00:19:03,554 --> 00:19:06,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is this the Eight-Six driver</i>
<i>and the fastest on Akina?</i></b></font>

312
00:19:06,384 --> 00:19:10,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is this the guy who defeated</i>
<i>Keisuke Takahashi's FD?</i></b></font>

313
00:19:11,494 --> 00:19:13,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you want?</b></font>

314
00:19:13,394 --> 00:19:14,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sir?</b></font>

315
00:19:16,364 --> 00:19:18,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fried tofu, please.</b></font>

316
00:19:18,004 --> 00:19:19,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Coming right up.</b></font>

317
00:19:19,534 --> 00:19:22,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What am I doing?!</i></b></font>

318
00:19:22,404 --> 00:19:24,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um... I...</b></font>

319
00:19:24,234 --> 00:19:26,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My name is Iketani,</b></font>

320
00:19:26,004 --> 00:19:29,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and I'm with a street racing team
called the Akina Speed Stars.</b></font>

321
00:19:32,314 --> 00:19:35,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The truth is, I heard this strange rumor</b></font>

322
00:19:35,884 --> 00:19:38,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that the fastest downhill driver on Mt. Akina</b></font>

323
00:19:38,224 --> 00:19:41,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is an Eight-Six driven by
the owner of a tofu shop.</b></font>

324
00:19:41,994 --> 00:19:46,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know who told you that, but it's not me.</b></font>

325
00:19:46,394 --> 00:19:48,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please don't play dumb!</b></font>

326
00:19:48,264 --> 00:19:53,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I searched the whole city, and this is
the only tofu shop with an Eight-Six!</b></font>

327
00:19:53,004 --> 00:19:55,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here you go. 140 yen.</b></font>

328
00:19:57,734 --> 00:19:59,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

329
00:19:59,374 --> 00:20:03,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well... I'm kind of in a tough situation.</b></font>

330
00:20:03,014 --> 00:20:06,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you please listen to what I have to say?</b></font>

331
00:20:06,044 --> 00:20:09,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a bother. Right in
the middle of my work...</b></font>

332
00:20:09,054 --> 00:20:12,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But you're not doing anything!
I'm the only customer here!</b></font>

333
00:20:13,554 --> 00:20:17,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was rude, saying something like that...</b></font>

334
00:20:17,224 --> 00:20:20,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry, but I'm desperate.</b></font>

335
00:20:20,694 --> 00:20:23,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The truth is, a team called the Akagi Red Suns</b></font>

336
00:20:23,394 --> 00:20:26,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>challenged us to a time attack battle.</b></font>

337
00:20:26,404 --> 00:20:30,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Red Suns have some drivers
with awesome technique.</b></font>

338
00:20:30,134 --> 00:20:33,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nobody on our team can compete with them.</b></font>

339
00:20:33,444 --> 00:20:38,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But since this is our mountain,
we definitely don't want to lose!</b></font>

340
00:20:38,044 --> 00:20:40,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So what do you want me to do?</b></font>

341
00:20:40,814 --> 00:20:45,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mr. Fujiwara... Please teach me
how to tackle Mt. Akina.</b></font>

342
00:20:49,394 --> 00:20:52,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's an impossible request.</b></font>

343
00:20:52,894 --> 00:20:56,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please! Even just enough to make
me a tenth of a second faster!</b></font>

344
00:20:56,494 --> 00:20:58,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I beg you!</b></font>

345
00:20:58,134 --> 00:20:59,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know how you feel,</b></font>

346
00:20:59,764 --> 00:21:03,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but driving technique cannot be
improved in two or three days.</b></font>

347
00:21:03,334 --> 00:21:06,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In order to make your car do what you want,</b></font>

348
00:21:06,744 --> 00:21:10,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you have to think continuously
and practice on your own.</b></font>

349
00:21:10,044 --> 00:21:12,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I was actively racing,</b></font>

350
00:21:12,184 --> 00:21:15,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was tackling Akina even in my dreams.</b></font>

351
00:21:15,254 --> 00:21:18,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Technique isn't something that can be taught.</b></font>

352
00:21:18,784 --> 00:21:21,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's something you find on your own.</b></font>

353
00:21:26,724 --> 00:21:30,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry... I can't help you.</b></font>

354
00:21:30,364 --> 00:21:33,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mr. Fujiwara, I'll be back again.</b></font>

355
00:21:51,384 --> 00:21:54,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>"Think continuously and</i>
<i>practice on your own..."</i></b></font>

356
00:21:54,384 --> 00:21:57,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've done that, but my times</i>
<i>haven't improved a bit.</i></b></font>

357
00:21:57,594 --> 00:21:59,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Why not?!</i></b></font>

358
00:22:02,534 --> 00:22:06,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dammit! No matter how hard I try,</i>
<i>I just can't understand it!</i></b></font>

359
00:22:10,774 --> 00:22:13,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't avoid it! Please! Get to the inside!</i></b></font>

360
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride says you gotta be wild and tough</i></b></font>

361
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sou tanin wa kaizai shinai</i></b></font>

362
00:22:48,544 --> 00:22:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never stop, tomaritakunai</i></b></font>

363
00:22:50,074 --> 00:22:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Gisei ni natta ai ga cry shite mo</i></b></font>

364
00:22:52,144 --> 00:22:53,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Peak mezashite, sweep the winding street</i></b></font>

365
00:22:53,944 --> 00:22:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beep beep! Keikokuon wa so cheap!</i></b></font>

366
00:22:56,154 --> 00:22:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sheep-tachi wa michi wo akero</i></b></font>

367
00:22:57,614 --> 00:23:00,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'Cuz I'm never gonna stop, streak my dream</i></b></font>

368
