390
00:24:26,504 --> 00:24:30,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Okay, today's guest is the stubborn</i>
<i>owner of the Fujiwara Tofu Shop,</i></b></font>

391
00:24:30,544 --> 00:24:33,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mr. Bunta Fujiwara.</i></b></font>

392
00:24:33,114 --> 00:24:35,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mr. Bunta, according to your theory,</i></b></font>

393
00:24:35,214 --> 00:24:37,414
