394
00:24:37,414 --> 00:24:40,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You must find it on your own, right?</i></b></font>

395
00:24:40,054 --> 00:24:44,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--That was really cool. I was impressed.</i>
